ssion over it arbitrary if not first hand (like Carl’s.)  So your BC friends may wish to take issue, but it will remain that there is not any STATISTICALLY significant evidence that this is a abhorrently detrimental procedure when properly performed, no matter how significant their personal experiences are to them.<br>
